聆听 Shed Seven 令人反思的新单曲“Starlings” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-shed-sevens-reflective-new-single-starlings-3525769?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-shed-sevens-reflective-new-单椋鸟Hollie GeraghtyMon, 30 Oct 2023 14:05:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3525769 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="L-R 保罗·阿德里安·班克斯 (Paul Adrian Banks) 吉他手兼主唱理查德·詹姆斯·“里克”·维特 (Richard James &quot;Rick&quot; Witter)" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “有些人可能会说这是黑暗的主题，但我发现它也非常令人振奋，”瑞克·威特 (Rick Witter) 分享道</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-shed-sevens-reflective-new-single-starlings-3525769">聆听 Shed Seven 的反思性新单曲“Starlings”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="L-R 保罗·阿德里安·班克斯 (Paul Adrian Banks) 吉他手兼主唱理查德·詹姆斯·“里克”·维特 (Richard James &quot;Rick&quot; Witter)" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shed-seven-starlings-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shed-seven">Shed Seven</a>分享了一首令人沉思的新单曲，名为“Starlings”——请听下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shed-seven-share-new-single-featuring-rowetta-and-talk-guest-heavy-album-a-matter-of-time-3505094">棚七分享由 Rowetta 主演的新单曲，并谈论客串较多的专辑“A Matter Of Time”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲是乐队即将发行的新专辑《A Matter of Time》的最新预览版（可在<a href="https://shedsevenn.lnk.to/AMOTPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处预订</a>），是继单曲《Kissing California》、《F:K:H》和上个月由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">Happy</a>主演的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shed-seven-share-new-single-featuring-rowetta-and-talk-guest-heavy-album-a-matter-of-time-3505094">In Ecstasy</a> 》之后的歌曲。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">周一</a>歌手罗维塔。</p><p>与他们最近的主打单曲相比，《Starlings》是一首更加忧郁的作品，以缓慢燃烧的弦乐和钢琴旋律以及关于痛苦但充满希望的告别的歌词为特色。</p><p>听下面的曲目。 </p><p><iframe title="七号棚 - 椋鸟（官方展示）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZprcQnpd_kA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>谈到新单曲，主唱 Rick Witter 表示：“《Starlings》以不同的情感展示了这张专辑。这是一封写给已故伴侣的情书。我有一个想法，一对夫妇从永远在一起，只是其中一个人去世了，剩下的伴侣基本上在原地踏步，直到他们可以在以太中永远团聚的时候到来。</p><p> “有些人可能会说这是黑暗的主题，但我发现它也非常令人振奋，而且比人们想象的更常见。”</p><p>他补充道：“美丽的琴弦和钢琴为这样一首衷心的歌曲添加了所需的一切。它充满怀旧和反思，但也有一种永恒的感觉。”</p><p>在去年的 Bingley Weekender 音乐节上<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">，The Libertines</a>主唱在舞台边跟着 The Libertines 的歌曲一起唱歌后，Shed Seven 主唱成功邀请<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">Pete Doherty</a>参与新专辑的闭幕曲《Throwaways》。</p><p> “我们在主舞台上在 The Libertines 之前演出，当我们在做演出时，我只是看着舞台的一侧，发现彼得和我的家人一起站在那里观看演出，他正在唱每一个字，”Witter <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shed-seven-share-new-single-featuring-rowetta-and-talk-guest-heavy-album-a-matter-of-time-3505094">在最近的一次采访中告诉<em>NME</em></a> 。</p><p> “所以当我们结束演出后，我走过去，他告诉我，在 90 年代——前浪荡子——他会拿着吉他坐在床上，学习 Shed Seven 的歌曲，我觉得这很酷。我只是说，‘看，我们已经有了这首歌，我们的唱片上还有另外几位嘉宾，我们不妨把船扔到这里，你想跳上来吗？’他说，‘我绝对愿意’。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-shed-sevens-reflective-new-single-starlings-3525769">聆听 Shed Seven 的反思性新单曲“Starlings”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Xbox 将阻止第三方控制器以“保留主机体验” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-will-block-third-party-controllers-to-preserve-the-console-experience-3525752?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=xbox-will-阻止第三方控制器以保留控制台体验Imogen DonovanMon, 30 Oct 2023 14:02:20 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsXboxXbox OneXbox Series SXbox Series XXbox Series X|S https://www.nme.com/?p=3525752 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “使用未经授权的配件会损害您的游戏体验”，阅读错误弹出窗口</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-will-block-third-party-controllers-to-preserve-the-console-experience-3525752">Xbox 将阻止第三方控制器以“保留主机体验”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>出于“性能、安全和安全”的考虑，从 11 月起，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>将不允许玩家在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox">Xbox</a>上使用未经授权的第三方控制器和配件。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-mountain-goats-john-darnielle-talks-magic-the-gathering-secret-lair-set-3483851">山羊乐队的约翰·达尼尔 (John Darnielle) 谈论为《万智牌》写预言</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.windowscentral.com/gaming/xbox/xboxs-new-policy-say-goodbye-to-unofficial-accessories-after-november" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Windows Central</em></a>在 10 月 29 日的一篇文章中报告称，玩家在附加第三方配件时遇到了错误“0x82d60002”。</p><p> “使用未经授权的配件会损害您的游戏体验。因此，未经授权的配件将于 2023 年 11 月 12 日被禁止使用。”控制台上的弹出窗口显示。然后，它建议玩家将产品退回商店或与制造商联系。 </p><figure id="attachment_3525788" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3525788" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3525788" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3525788" class="wp-caption-text"> Xbox 控制器 图片来源：Jose Gil 来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>微软在向<a href="https://www.gamesindustry.biz/xbox-will-block-unauthorized-third-party-controllers" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>GamesIndustry.biz</em></a>提供的一份声明中解释说，该错误实际上是其新政策的一部分，该政策将于 11 月 17 日起在全球范围内推出。</p><p> “微软和其他获得许可的 Xbox 硬件合作伙伴的配件是按照性能、安全和安全的质量标准设计和制造的，”它表示。</p><p> “未经授权的配件可能会影响 Xbox 主机（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-one">Xbox One</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X/S</a> ）上的游戏体验。游戏玩家可能会收到一条弹出警告，表明其配件未经授权。</p><p> “最终，未经授权的配件将被禁止使用，以保持游戏机的游戏体验。有关 Xbox 主机支持的配件的完整列表，请访问 www.xbox.com/accessories。”</p><p>接受<em>Windows Central</em>采访的消息人士表示，微软正试图通过这一举措让官方第三方控制器的制造变得更加容易。 </p><figure id="attachment_3525791" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3525791" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3525791" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unauthorised-xbox-controllers-not-going-to-work-after-november-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3525791" class="wp-caption-text"> Xbox 控制器 图片来源：Kamil S via Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>这样，新的控制器将被允许使用与 Xbox 配合使用的无线功能，可能是通过在控制器内部放置安全芯片来实现的。然而，如果没有得到微软的批准，那些已经存在的产品就将终结。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-finals"><em>《The Finals》</em></a>因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-finals-sloppy-ai-voice-acting-criticised-by-voice-actors-3525621">使用人工智能为其评论员和参赛者配音而</a>受到批评，尽管开发人员解释说，这“让[团队]在质量方面走得足够远”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-will-block-third-party-controllers-to-preserve-the-console-experience-3525752">Xbox 将阻止第三方控制器以“保留主机体验”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
