reviews/film-reviews/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-concert-movie-3513715">一部新的音乐会电影</a>，并将在未来几个月内参加无数的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-international-dates-for-eras-tour-3458456">国际演出</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-is-officially-a-billionaire-say-reports-3523898">据报道正式成为亿万富翁</a>。</p><p>上周（10 月 26 日）这位流行歌星的财富最新公布， <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2023-taylor-swift-net-worth-billionaire/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>彭博社</em></a>的一份新报告详细列出了她的估计净资产。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/imogen-heap-shares-studio-photos-from-1989-taylors-version-session-3525771">Imogen Heap 分享“1989（泰勒版）”会议的工作室照片的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
